trying to hustle me

01:51.023 --> 01:52.373
so I can make a few bucks.

01:52.416 --> 01:54.810
Hustle you? Oh, come on,
Calvin, that's crazy.

01:54.853 --> 01:56.942
Oh. You want
to hear some crazy? Okay.

01:56.986 --> 01:58.857
You see that
house down there?

01:58.901 --> 02:01.208
