and Marty on their taxes

02:01.251 --> 02:02.731
six years straight.

02:05.125 --> 02:06.387
And see those wires
hanging from there?

02:06.430 --> 02:09.651
That guy is stealing the
other family's cable.

02:09.694 --> 02:12.480
But they're running
an illegal day care,

02:12.523 --> 02:14.656
so they can't say nothing
about it.

02:14.699 --> 02:17.093
Oh, man, I thought
that was a beauty salon.

02:17.137 --> 02:18.486
Oh, yeah, they do that, too.

02:18.529 --> 02:21.097
Look, man,

02:21.141 --> 02:23.099
everybody around here's
just trying to get by.

02:23.143 --> 02:26.058
I just don't want them
getting by on me.

02:26.102 --> 02:28.235
Well, I guess that's how
you and I are different, Calvin.

02:28.278 --> 02:30.933
I choose to believe that
the world isn't out to get me.

02:30.976 --> 02:32.761
Okay. You come see me

02:32.804 --> 02:35.285
