cosigned for a motorcycle.

02:35.329 --> 02:37.896
Yard sale.

02:37.940 --> 02:41.161
All right, man. I will
tell you, you know,

02:41.204 --> 02:44.686
last yard sale I had,
I cleared a cool grand.

02:44.729 --> 02:46.035
Hold on, hold up.

02:47.384 --> 02:49.038
You made 1,000 bucks?

02:49.081 --> 02:50.082
Oh, yeah. That's right.

02:50.126 --> 02:52.084
Well, ahoy, Dave.

02:53.956 --> 02:56.915
'Cause I know my crap's got
to be worth more than your crap.

02:56.959 --> 02:58.787
I'm having me a yard sale.

02:58.830 --> 03:00.354
Well, you know, I'm
happy to help out.

03:00.397 --> 03:01.790
Well, thank you.

03:01.833 --> 03:03.835
And in return,
I'm gonna do you a solid.

03:03.879 --> 03:07.187
You see that extension cord
running from your attic window?Yeah.

03:07.230 --> 03:09.450
