to the day care.

03:11.930 --> 03:13.845
♪ Welcome to the block,
welcome to the neighborhood ♪

03:13.889 --> 03:15.151
♪ Welcome to the hood.

03:19.721 --> 03:21.766
Ooh, this is gonna be great.
I can't wait to meet

03:21.810 --> 03:24.943
more of our neighbors.Me, neither.
