Washington and Jackson.

03:28.382 --> 03:30.210
All right, Pop.

03:30.253 --> 03:32.603
Here you go. Good luck
with your yard sale, bro.

03:32.647 --> 03:34.605
Hold on, whoa.
Where are you going?

03:34.649 --> 03:35.998
I was going to the library.

03:36.041 --> 03:38.870
Oh, no. No, you and Marty
are in charge of security.

03:38.914 --> 03:40.611
What?

03:40.655 --> 03:42.222
Well, what's it pay?

03:42.265 --> 03:43.658
Room and board.

03:45.050 --> 03:47.009
Fine, I'll start today.

03:47.052 --> 03:50.099
Do I get a weapon?Sure. Yeah.

03:50.142 --> 03:51.100
