03:52.449 --> 03:54.538
Don't be afraid
to use them.

03:54.582 --> 03:56.236
Oh, great, Pop.
If a bowl of soup

03:56.279 --> 03:58.368
tries to steal
something, I'm ready.

04:00.196 --> 04:02.851
Hey, you guys.
We picked you up some coffee

