you got you a car seat.

05:39.991 --> 05:41.297
Throw some sandwiches in there,

05:41.341 --> 05:44.822
you going to a picnic.
Hmm? Look.

05:44.866 --> 05:47.695
Calvin, this is
the best yard sale

05:47.738 --> 05:49.261
