all day.

06:09.412 --> 06:11.153
You know, I've
actually been having

06:11.196 --> 06:12.415
a pretty good time, myself.Uh-huh.

06:12.459 --> 06:15.026
I sold everything
on table two,

06:15.070 --> 06:17.289
and then I sold table two.

06:17.333 --> 06:19.422
Oh, oh, man! Well,
what's your secret?

06:19.466 --> 06:20.554
Watch and learn.

06:20.597 --> 06:24.514
Hey, you know,
just so you know,

06:24.558 --> 06:26.560
this grill used to
belong to Tupac.

06:27.604 --> 06:30.259
Yeah, he made a
