06:30.302 --> 06:32.870
You know, one time
he had a barbecue,

06:32.914 --> 06:34.437
and he didn't invite
Biggie, and...

06:34.481 --> 06:36.047
Well, you know the rest.

06:37.092 --> 06:38.528
Oh, okay.

06:40.312 --> 06:42.314
Ah!

06:43.664 --> 06:46.057
Calvin, what're you doing?

06:46.101 --> 06:48.277
