for money.

06:48.320 --> 06:51.323
Well, yeah. I mean, I wouldn't
lie to him for no reason.

06:51.367 --> 06:53.325
That would be messed up.

06:56.111 --> 06:57.765
Uh, hey, Marty.

06:57.808 --> 07:00.637
What is with
the sunglasses, bro?

07:00.681 --> 07:02.465
It's a little security
trick I picked up

07:02.509 --> 07:04.119
so nobody can see
where I'm looking.

07:04.162 --> 07:05.773
Right now I got my eye
on that guy over there

07:05.816 --> 07:07.383
licking the
nine-volt batteries.

07:09.907 --> 07:11.909
You know, that's nothing.

07:11.953 --> 07:14.564
A minute ago he was licking
the sewing machine.

07:14.608 --> 07:17.175
Yeah, I better go
shut that down.

07:17.219 --> 07:21.528
Hey, man! Store policy:
you lick it, you buy it.

07:21.571 --> 07:24.226
How you doing,
Miss Simpson?

07:24.269 --> 07:26.315
Well, I'm still
above ground, ain't I?

07:27.795 --> 07:30.493
Listen, how much y'all want
for this porcelain angel?

07:30.537 --> 07:34.541
Well, you know, there's a very
special story about this angel.

07:34.584 --> 07:35.933
When...Cut the crap.

07:38.022 --> 07:39.546
I'll give you
three dollars for it.

07:39.589 --> 07:41.199
How about
four dollars?

07:41.243 --> 07:42.418
How about two dollars?

07:42.462 --> 07:45.987
Okay. Fine, two dollars.

07:46.030 --> 07:48.206
Okay.
Here's a dollar.

07:50.948 --> 07:53.429
You know this is
a Canadian dollar.

07:56.388 --> 07:58.390
Oh, this is awesome.

07:58.434 --> 08:01.306
This is so much fun.
